{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c7fbd3774c","title":"河南省文联文学座谈会与会者〈呼吁书〉","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6b25c6b059","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":28,"articleId":"c7fbd3774c"}],"tags":[{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"90e79316bd","name":"栾星"},{"id":"9ec5840208","name":"河南"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"56235c3610","type":"title","text":"河南省文联文学座谈会与会者〈呼吁书〉","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7fbd3774c"},{"id":"4498340770","type":"authors","text":"河南栾星","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7fbd3774c"},{"id":"d39a116fd4","type":"subtitle","text":"(栾星：作家，河南省文联创作部主任)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7fbd3774c"},{"id":"f020daae5e","type":"paragraph","text":"编者注：这是马长风右派集团发动的，得到苏金伞右派集团积极支持的，最后并由栾星起草的，在右派分子把持下的河南省文联文学座谈会上通过的〈呼吁书〉全文。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7fbd3774c"},{"id":"dd011d79ce","type":"paragraph","text":"中共河南省委员会：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7fbd3774c"},{"id":"d011697a58","type":"paragraph","text":"河南人民检察院：","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7fbd3774c"},{"id":"38bfbffc45","type":"paragraph","text":"我们为马炳玉同志呼吁！","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7fbd3774c"},{"id":"8cc629d1b1","type":"paragraph","text":"马炳玉同志是郑州铁路局的一位工人业余作者。由于业余从事文学创作，在“肃反”运动中，遭到严重的非法刑询与拷打，致成残疾，至今一年有余，尚未恢复健康。听了马炳玉同志在座谈会上的陈述，我们一致对造成这一不幸事件应负主要责任的违法乱纪分子，表示愤慨。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7fbd3774c"},{"id":"f721e2998b","type":"paragraph","text":"为此，特建议省委及检察部门迅速的严肃处理这一事件，以平民愤。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7fbd3774c"},{"id":"effb7d3ff9","type":"paragraph","text":"一、建议你们联合组织检察组，检查事件原委，对马炳玉事件作出公正结论；对违犯党纪国法、打人成性的分子，予以严肃制裁。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7fbd3774c"},{"id":"a493a11a1f","type":"paragraph","text":"二、对马炳玉同志予以安抚，赔偿其全部物质损失；即送医疗机构疗治，其医疗费用，应由铁路局全部负责，在医疗期间其工资全部照发。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7fbd3774c"},{"id":"b054b922c0","type":"paragraph","text":"三、建议将处理结果公诸报端，或通过省文联转告所有与会同志。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7fbd3774c"},{"id":"e973898cde","type":"paragraph","text":"最后，我们对省委在处理这一事件中的拖沓作风，表示遗憾。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7fbd3774c"},{"id":"3f36befc8f","type":"paragraph","text":"我们忠心拥护党，因而文不饰词，直言以陈。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7fbd3774c"},{"id":"62c5fb5272","type":"paragraph","text":"此致！","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7fbd3774c"},{"id":"2c62774fe9","type":"appellation","text":"敬礼","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7fbd3774c"},{"id":"f0607453ee","type":"paragraph","text":" 河南省文联文学座谈会全体与会作者一九五七年五月二十八日(附签名一份)","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7fbd3774c"},{"id":"27e75b5493","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《苏金伞右派集团言论与作品》（河南省文学美术工作者联合会，1958年）。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7fbd3774c"}],"page":{"id":"3209f6c0e1","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7fbd3774c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}